ing: 4 firm bananas, peeled and cut into 1- to 2-inch pieces
des: "A simple, quick dessert to serve over vanilla ice cream."
ins: Melt butter in a wok over high heat. Add bananas, brown sugar, and cinnamon; saute until bananas are golden brown and sugar is bubbling, about 5 minutes. Stir in sesame seeds and lime juice.
